# Streamlit Cloud secrets template

Copy into: Streamlit Cloud → App → Settings → Secrets

Cloud cannot reach localhost Splunk — use mock mode for the public judge URL.
Record your YouTube demo locally with Splunk + MCP running.

```toml
SPLUNK_USE_MOCK = "true"
SPLUNK_HOST = "localhost"
SPLUNK_PORT = "8089"
SPLUNK_TOKEN = ""
SPLUNK_OFFICIAL_MCP_URL = "https://localhost:8089/services/mcp"
SPLUNK_MCP_BRIDGE_URL = "http://localhost:8765"
CHROMA_PERSIST_DIR = ".chroma"
PROPOSER_MODEL = "claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022"
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY = "optional"
```
